content.rendered:
Directed by Akshay Anand

Written by Ajit Rajpal

Cast Muntazir Ahmad. Akshay Anand (Ajay Suryavanshi). Kabir Bedi (Shera). Hitesh Bharadwaj (Hitesh (as Hitesh Bhardwaj)). Abhay Bhargava (Abhay). Ravi Raj Kande (Chandrakaant). Dawood Khan (Prosoner). Viju Khote (Viju Khote). Yogendra Kumeria (Tharki producer). Usha Nadkarni (Aaji). Chetna Pande (Sheetal). Dayashankar Pandey (Akash Dubey (as Daya Shankar Pandey)). Raghu Raja (Raghu). Jaswant Singh Rathore (Rangeela). Sushant Saxena (Shera’s Son). Abhishek Sharma (Abhishek Naik). Vikram Shankar Singh (Jidah (as Vikram Singh)). Yashwant Singh (Rangeela). Sunil Vishrani (Music Company Owner)

Languages Hindi

Producers Raghu Bhatia. Vishal Bhatia. Pradip Khairwar. Raghu Raja. Daityari Sa. Jagbir Singh

Production NeelRishiFilm
